FBIS4-42258 "drweu105_p_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-105 Daily Report 31 May 1994 GREECE Defense Minister Visits Albanian Border Posts Defense Minister Visits Albanian Border Posts NC3105122394 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 1130 GMT 31 May 94 NC3105122394 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] National Defense Minister Yerasimos Arsenis today is visiting the town of Kastoria and the Dhipotamia guard post on the Greek-Albanian border. Shortly before his departure for the Greek-Albanian border region, Mr. Arsenis said that this visit had been schedule long ago and that his intention is to visit not only the Greek-Albanian borders but also other border areas. Mr. Arsenis said: Of course, this visit is taking place at a time of tension in Greek-Albanian relations, but my task is to ascertain that the Armed Forces will do their duty by being vigilant and guarding the area.
